metadata.title: Safety Depot MP40-GREY PROFESSIONAL GREY MESH VEST (MEDIUM)
features: Four pockets on outer portion of vest (Two on the upper chest two on the lower waist)
Two inside pockets on the lower waist
description: Safety Depot offers this breathable jacket with Pen Divider and High Visibility Reflective tape. The vest is made of 100% Polyester Mesh that comes with four pockets on its outer portion (Two on the upper chest two on the lower waist) and two inside pockets on the lower waist. This is NON-ANSI compliant, which is suitable for use in the warehouse, school, landscaping industry, or any profession that does not require ANSI-certified vests.
